--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.0.0 (2019-01-24)
C: Rename option 'restic_monitor_mail_recipient' to 'restic_monitor_mail_from_address'
C: Rename option 'restic_monitor_mail_sender' to 'restic_monitor_mail_to_address'

* Version 1.1.2 (2019-01-22)
E: Improve script by throwing error message if script is executed interactively

* Version 1.1.1 (2019-01-21)
E: Improve script and reduce noise by removing echo command from alerting function

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-01-07)
F: Update to restic version '0.9.4'

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-12-13)
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-12)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.5.4 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove 'restic_monitor_mail_subject' parameter

* Version 0.5.3 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove email information from message

* Version 0.5.2 (2018-12-04)
B: Fix 'limit-download' and 'limit-upload' variables in script

* Version 0.5.1 (2018-11-27)
E: Minor style improvements

* Version 0.5.0 (2018-11-18)
F: Add support for 'limit-download' option (restic_limit_download)
F: Add support for 'limit-upload' option (restic_limit_upload)

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-10-21)
F: Update to restic version '0.9.3'

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-09-14)
E: Add 'no_log' parameter to sensitive tasks

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-08-30)
F: Update to restic version '0.9.2'

* Version 0.2.5 (2018-08-28)
E: Ensure user's home directory is being removed during remove sequence

* Version 0.2.4 (2018-07-21)
B: Fix remove tags

* Version 0.2.3 (2018-07-19)
B: Ensure group and user is being removed in 'remove' state
B: Add missing 'bzip2' dependency required for binary installation

* Version 0.2.2 (2018-07-19)
E: Shell script improvements

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-07-12)
B: Correct owner and group of backup folder

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-07-12)
F: Add group and user 'restic'
F: Add backup folder '/backup/restic'
E: Generate a random minute for the cronjob
E: Minor role improvements

* Version 0.1.5 (2018-07-10)
B: Fix 'date_time' in log header

* Version 0.1.4 (2018-07-10)
E: Enable quiet mode for SSH connections

* Version 0.1.3 (2018-07-10)
B: Add missing 'backup_server' and 'backup_user' parameters

* Version 0.1.2 (2018-07-10)
B: Ensure log file is created if nonexistent

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-07-10)
E: Exclude 'restic' backup folder

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-07-10)
F: Initial release
